<body><div><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">为构建和谐、法治、健康的网络环境，维护</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">平台秩序，更好的保障用户合法权益，</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">依据并贯彻 《全国人民代表大会常务委员会关于加强网络信息保护的决定》的文件精神，与用户共同制定本公约。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第一章 总 则</span></h4><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第一条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">是由</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">深圳江月何年文化传媒有限公司</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">创建的社区平台(下称本平台)。本公约是用户与 </span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">社区（以下称“</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">”）之间的协议，</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">将按照本公约之内容为用户提供服务。本公约所述条款为用户使用</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">平台的先决条件。用户的继续使用行为将视作对本公约全部条款的完全接受。若用户不同意本公约中所述条款或</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">对后续条款的修改，用户应不使用或主动消取相关服务。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户是指注册</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">的用户，其行为需遵守本公约；未注册者在本平台的活动亦参照本公约。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户在本平台的活动不得违反现行法律法规。因用户在</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">中提交的信息含有以下违反法律法规、相关政策的信息或者内容造成不利影响的，由用户直接承担责任，如因此给</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">造成不利后果的，用户应负责消除影响，并赔偿因此导致的一切损失。本平台将按照相关法律法规及用户注册协议，配合司法机关维护被侵权人合法权益。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二章 用户权利</span></h4><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第四条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户享有</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">帐号的使用权。该使用权不得以任何方式转让，帐号的行为将被视为注册用户的行为。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第五条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户在本平台的表达不得侵害他人合法权益，不得与中华人民共和国现行法律法规和本公约相冲突。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第六条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户的个人隐私受到保护。</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">的用户真实身份信息由第三方平台保存。对用户隐私的保护是</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">的基本政策，用户自行公开、司法机关依照法定程序要求披露的除外。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第七条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户在</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">的正当权益受到侵害时，可通过</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">举报功能或司法途径维护合法权益。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三章 用户行为规范</span></h4><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第八条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户注册、使用</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">应符合现行法律法规。不得以任何方式受让</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">帐号使用权，不得盗用他人帐号。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第九条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户不得恶意通过机器或软件等非人力手段注册</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">帐号、发布内容或关注他人，经</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">官方许可的软件应用除外。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户拥有设置个性化帐号信息的权利(包括：昵称、头像、等)，但不得设置含有以下内容的帐号信息：</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(一) 违反国家法律法规的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(二) 包含人身攻击性质内容的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(三) 暗示与他人或机构相混同的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(四) 包含其他非法信息的。不得使用隐晦表达等方式规避以上限制。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十一条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户拥有发布信息的权利，但不得发布含有以下内容的信息：</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(一) 反对宪法确定的基本原则的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(二) 危害国家统一、主权和领土完整的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(三) 泄露国家秘密、危害国家安全或者损害国家荣誉和利益的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(四) 煽动民族仇恨、民族歧视，破坏民族团结，或者侵害民族风俗、习惯的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(五) 破坏国家宗教政策，宣扬邪教、迷信的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(六) 散布谣言，扰乱社会秩序，破坏社会稳定的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(七) 宣扬淫秽、赌博、暴力、色情、凶杀、恐怖或者教唆犯罪的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(八) 煽动非法集会、结社、游行、示威、聚众扰乱社会秩序的；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(九) 有法律、行政法规和国家规定禁止的其他内容的。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十二条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户不得发布不安全信息。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">不安全信息，包括可能对用户财产安全或信息安全造成损失的内容，主要表现为：</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">1.含钓鱼网站链接的相关内容；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">2.含木马、病毒网站链接及相关内容；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">3.含潜在危险、窃取用户隐私等相关内容；</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">4.影响用户体验或被大量用户举报的未经审核的外链、二维码及其他多媒体等内容；</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十三条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户不得发布垃圾营销信息。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">垃圾营销信息，是指以营利为目的，在与用户建立或维持关系的过程中，所产生的影响用户体验，扰乱社区秩序的信息和行为，其中包括垃圾信息、恶意行为和骚扰用户的营销信息，主要表现为：</span></p><ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">从事买卖粉丝及相关业务；</span></p><ol start="2" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">从事刷评论、刷搜索、刷投票、刷有奖活动业务；</span></p><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">通过机器或软件等非人力手段对他人页面大量发送广告信息；</span></p><ol start="4" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">虚假中奖信息；</span></p><ol start="5" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">机器抓取发送的无意义内容、重复内容；</span></p><ol start="6" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">利用系统漏洞干扰</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">正常秩序的行为。如：盗用他人账号、强制他人关注等；</span></p><ol start="7" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">影响用户体验或被大量用户举报的，其性质属于推销宣传推广的营销信息。</span></p><ol start="8" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十四条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户不应发布不实信息。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">发布不实信息。不实信息主要表现为：</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(一) 整体失实：事件本身系子虚乌有。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(二) 捏造细节：捏造细节使整个事件被扭曲。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(三) 图文不符：通过错误的图文搭配误导他人。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(四) 夸大事实：在描述中对事实夸大其词，误导他人。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(五) 过期信息：将已得到解决的事件作为新消息发布，并略去已产生的结果。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(六) 信息残缺：隐藏部分事实，以不完整的信息误导他人。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(七) 断章取义：将部分事实加上推测作为事实发布。文艺评论不适用本条规定。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十五条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户不得发布含有色情、淫秽及暗示性色情内容的文章、图片。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十六条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户应尊重他人名誉权，不得以侮辱、诽谤等方式对他人进行人身攻击。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十七条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户应尊重他人隐私权，不得侵害他人隐私。涉及公众利益或经由当事人同意的除外。隐私包括真实姓名、身份证号、电话号码、家庭住址及用户不愿公开的其他个人信息。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十八条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户应尊重他人肖像权，未经他人同意不得擅自使用或修改其肖像。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十九条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户应尊重他人安宁权，不得骚扰他人。不应以评论、私信、等方式对他人反复发送重复、近似、诉求相同的信息。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户应尊重他人著作权。转载发布他人原创内容需先获取原创作者授权，并且在发布时注明出处或带有明显转载标识。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第四章 平台管理</span></h4><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十一条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">平台管理由站方和用户群众共同完成。在任何情况下，如</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">合理地认为用户的行为可能违反上述法律、法规，可以在任何时候，不经事先通知终止向该用户提供服务。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十二条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">站方可通过主动发现及接受用户举报发现违规行为，每个</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户可使用</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">的举报功能。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十三条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">站方监督人员根据此条约处理违规行为。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十四条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">违规处理包括：内容处理和帐号处理。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">内容处理包括：删除、屏蔽、移除屏蔽</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">帐号处理包括：删除、封锁、移除封锁</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十五条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">对于可明显识别的违规行为，由站方直接处理；其他违规行为，由用户群众判定后处理。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第五章 侵权管理</span></h4><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十六条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户发布内容被举报后，</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">官方将会与原创作者进行核实；确认该用户是否获得授权</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">如确认该用户并未获得原创作者授权，我们将会针对该话题进行处理，处理方式：</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">1.对该条侵权内容进行屏蔽/删除操作，同时通知该用户所发布的哪条话题内容属于侵权内容；该话题内容已经被删除/屏蔽。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第六章 附 则</span></h4><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十七条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户需独立对自己在</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">上实施的行为承担法律责任。</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">有权对不符合本公约的用户行为作出独立处理，且在无需事先通知及/或征得用户同意的情况下采取但不限于屏蔽、删帖、停用账号等处理措施。因</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">中行为引发的法律纠纷，与</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">深圳江月何年文化传媒有限公司</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">无关。用户纠纷类违规，主要包括：</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(一) 泄露他人隐私，主要表现为：</span></p><ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">泄露身份信息：公开他人真实姓名及身份证号、电话号码、家庭住址。用户已公开或授权公开的除外，涉及公共利益的除外。</span></p><ol start="2" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">泄露其它信息：公开他人不愿被知悉的不危害社会的信息。如：性取向、生理及心理缺陷、财产状况、信用卡、电子消费卡、上网卡、上网帐号和密码、交易账号和密码、网上购物使用的帐号和密码、IP地址、浏览网页的踪迹或活动内容、私生活镜头以及社会关系等，他人可通过合法公开渠道得知的或涉及公共利益的除外。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(二) 人身攻击，主要表现为：</span></p><ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">侮辱：以侮辱性言论伤害他人。</span></p><ol start="2" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">诽谤：刻意捏造信息破坏他人名誉。误解不适用本条规定。</span></p><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.11pt; padding-left:3.89pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">肖像篡改：修改他人肖像且令本人不能接受。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(三) 冒充他人，主要表现为：通过头像、昵称、域名及各类自我说明，暗示自己与他人或机构相等同或有关联。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(四) 内容抄袭，主要表现为：发布他人原创内容而不注明出处或标识转载。</span></p><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">(五) 骚扰他人，主要表现为：以评论、私信、等方式对他人反复发送重复、近似、诉求相同的信息。反复是指3次及以上。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十八条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">本公约所指法律法规均指中华人民共和国大陆地区的现行法律法规。本公约与法律法规相冲突的，以法律法规的相关规定为准。因与中华人民共和国现行法律相抵触而导致部分无效的，不影响其他部分的效力。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十九条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">站方可依照互联网发展的不同阶段，随着平台管理经验的不断丰富，出于维护</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">夜飞鹊</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">平台秩序的目的，不断完善本公约。</span></p><h4 style="font-size:13.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:13.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十条</span></h4><p style="font-size:10pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">本公约自201</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">9</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">年</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">1</span><span style="font-family:苹方-简; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">月17日起施行，解释权归本平台所有。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div><div class="cnzz" style="display: none;">
